<p>lined with ovens or furnaces.  It appears to be safe from his favourite shell about here, which is the grass-cutter.</p>
<p>This is a shrapnel shell which has so sensitive a detonator that it explodes immediately on touching the ground or anything hard.  Thus a deadly spray of pellets is shot all round near to the ground.  If one hit a roof I imaging it would hardly affect the ground floor.</p>
<p>Restless night, &amp; was called out at 6.30 am for a case. After that we have been kept busy at intervals</p>
